<task id="WCWE-014" project="UI Create Wizard Enhancements R1">
  <metadata>
    <title>Move SecureProjectSection to top of CreateProject Enter Info step</title>
    <phase>2</phase>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>1 hour</estimated-effort>
    <tags>frontend, shared-library, wizard</tags>
    <dependencies>none</dependencies>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    E-10: Move the SecureProjectSection from below the form grid to above it in the
    CreateProject wizard's "Enter Info" step. The secure project toggle should be the
    first thing users see when entering project details, not buried below the form fields.
  </prompt>

  <role>Senior frontend developer with expertise in Fluent UI v9, React, and shared component libraries</role>

  <goal>The Secure Project toggle appears at the top of the "Enter Info" step in CreateProjectWizard, above all form fields.</goal>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Changes to shared wizard components must be made in @spaarke/ui-components, not in consuming Code Pages.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-012.md</file>
      <file>src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/CreateProjectWizard/</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      UAT feedback indicated that the Secure Project toggle in CreateProject is too easy to
      miss when placed below the form grid. Users creating confidential projects need to see
      and set this option immediately. Moving it to the top of the step ensures visibility
      and aligns with the workflow expectation that security classification happens first.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      No task dependencies. This is a layout-only change within the existing CreateProject
      wizard component.
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="locate-component">Read CreateProjectWizard "Enter Info" step component to find the SecureProjectSection placement.</step>
    <step order="2" name="move-section">Move the SecureProjectSection JSX block from below the form grid to above it, before the first form field.</step>
    <step order="3" name="verify-spacing">Ensure proper spacing between SecureProjectSection and the form grid below it using Fluent v9 tokens.</step>
    <step order="4" name="build-verify">Run npm build in the shared library to verify compilation.</step>
  </steps>

  <outputs>
    <output type="code">src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/CreateProjectWizard/ (modified — SecureProjectSection moved)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">SecureProjectSection renders above all form fields in the "Enter Info" step</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Visual spacing between SecureProjectSection and form fields is consistent with other wizard steps</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Toggle functionality (secure/unsecure) still works correctly after repositioning</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Shared library builds without errors</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
